eight=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080670/extras/eef8ee923267f39a5fb39876fd05b14a.webm?t=1721987189\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080670/extras/eef8ee923267f39a5fb39876fd05b14a.mp4?t=1721987189\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Adaptive Soundtrack: Experience a dynamic audio journey that evolves with your gameplay. In puzzle mode, relax with a thoughtful ambiance and slowed-down tracks, allowing you to strategize at your own pace. In rhythm mode, feel the adrenaline surge as the beat intensifies, driving the action forward. The soundtrack adapts seamlessly to each level type!</li></ul>",
